WEBVTT

00:00:33.840 --> 00:00:40.600
In terms of life, In terms of life's experience, we can categorize the fires 

00:00:40.600 --> 00:00:44.960
into three forms within us. 

00:00:45.960 --> 00:00:50.759
One is known as jataragni.

00:00:50.759 --> 00:00:59.759
Jatara literally means stomach or the digestive process 

00:00:59.759 --> 00:01:02.759
the digestive fire. 

00:01:02.759 --> 00:01:08.719
Without a little bit of fire in your belly, you cannot digest the food that you eat because 

00:01:08.719 --> 00:01:11.920
the food is just functioning as fuel 

00:01:11.920 --> 00:01:15.000
and you need to break down the fuel 

00:01:15.000 --> 00:01:22.200
to release the energy that's needed. So, there is a digestive fire going on. 

00:01:22.200 --> 00:01:30.760
If this digestive fire is well-nourished or well supplied with fuel, 

00:01:30.760 --> 00:01:38.599
it also becomes reproductive fire. So, these two dimensions of 

00:01:38.599 --> 00:01:49.239
digestion and reproductive fire, together we can call them as jataragni. 

00:01:49.239 --> 00:01:56.480
If your jataragni is strong, if you've maintained your jataragni well, 

00:01:56.480 --> 00:02:02.040
you will have a robust body.

00:02:02.040 --> 00:02:07.680
The other dimension is called chitagni.

00:02:07.680 --> 00:02:12.919
In between, there are various classifications but 

00:02:12.919 --> 00:02:15.560
I don't want to complicate your existence, I'm making it 

00:02:15.560 --> 00:02:19.319
simple for you. One is physical, another is 

00:02:19.319 --> 00:02:24.120
the dimension of the mind and beyond. It's called chitagni. 

00:02:24.120 --> 00:02:28.520
If you move to the next dimension of the fire, 

00:02:28.520 --> 00:02:34.120
which is called bhootagni – that is elemental fire

00:02:34.120 --> 00:02:39.680
if your elemental fire is on, you will see that 

00:02:39.680 --> 00:02:44.800
the circus of the body and mind doesn't make much sense to you. 

00:02:44.800 --> 00:02:50.400
Your interest and your focus will completely shift to another dimension

00:02:50.400 --> 00:02:55.919
of creation. More fundamental aspect of creation 

00:02:55.919 --> 00:03:01.080
as to the very way life is happening rather than 

00:03:01.080 --> 00:03:09.759
being entertained by the antics of the body and the mind. 

00:03:09.759 --> 00:03:15.479
So, these three aspects – if one takes charge of jataragni, 

00:03:15.479 --> 00:03:21.319
you have a healthy and robust body, if you take charge of your chitagni, 

00:03:21.319 --> 00:03:26.479
you have a mind which will find 

00:03:26.479 --> 00:03:32.159
many uses of course, but if you have 

00:03:32.159 --> 00:03:36.719
mastery or some 

00:03:36.719 --> 00:03:42.639
ability to manage your bhootagni, then you have 

00:03:42.639 --> 00:03:48.840
fundamental mastery over life process.

00:03:48.840 --> 00:03:56.360
Beyond this, there is something called as sarvagni because

00:03:56.360 --> 00:04:01.039
the physical dimension of the existence 

00:04:01.039 --> 00:04:08.120
or the physical dimension of this universe or the creation, 

00:04:08.120 --> 00:04:14.159
as… according to modern science is less than two percent. 

00:04:14.159 --> 00:04:21.759
So, if you know the entire universe, you know two percent of the existence. 

00:04:21.759 --> 00:04:28.439
So, sarvagni is that dimension which touches 

00:04:28.439 --> 00:04:32.720
where there is no elements, where there is no creation 

00:04:32.720 --> 00:04:40.360
as you know it, or in other words, where there is no physical nature. 

00:04:40.360 --> 00:04:44.759
Generally,

00:04:44.759 --> 00:04:54.160
 a yogi, who wants to access the nature of life, 

00:04:54.160 --> 00:04:59.560
will not interest himself in jataragni, 

00:04:59.560 --> 00:05:03.680
chitagni, bhootagni. 

00:05:03.680 --> 00:05:09.920
He will focus only on sarvagni because 

00:05:10.040 --> 00:05:12.079
this is the ultimate fire 

00:05:12.079 --> 00:05:17.120
but it's a very cool fire. It does not burn like jataragni. 

00:05:17.120 --> 00:05:22.800
It's a very obvious fire – the digestive fires. 

00:05:22.800 --> 00:05:27.399
Chitagni is not so obvious but very much there.

00:05:27.399 --> 00:05:32.920
Bhootagni – not so visible at all but very much there. 

00:05:32.920 --> 00:05:39.759
Sarvagni almost feels like it's absent but without it, nothing would happen. 

00:05:39.759 --> 00:05:43.839
It's a fundamental fire or it's the ultimate fire 

00:05:43.839 --> 00:05:47.800
which holds all other fires within it.

